## â–¶ï¸ Running the Projects

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Tanveer-hub570/My-Portfolio.git
```

2. Navigate into any project folder:
```bash
cd A2\ API\ Integration
```

3. Start Expo Go:
```bash
npm install
npx expo start
```

4. Scan the QR code using **Expo Go** app on your mobile device.

